mysql> select*from stud2 where marks>(select avg(marks) from stud2);
+-------+---------+----------+-------+------------+------------+
| regno | name    | courseno | marks | facultydoj | assesments |
+-------+---------+----------+-------+------------+------------+
|     1 | nithish |        1 |    70 |       2001 |          6 |
|     2 | ram     |        2 |    50 |       2002 |          5 |
+-------+---------+----------+-------+------------+------------+
2 rows in set (0.11 sec)

