mysql> select courseno,marks from stud2 where marks>(select avg(marks) from stud2)order by courseno;
+----------+-------+
| courseno | marks |
+----------+-------+
|        1 |    70 |
|        2 |    50 |
+----------+-------+
2 rows in set (0.00 sec)
